Description
Corrected installation via Homebrew instructions. (In the current instructions, the command given searches for an unrelated cask called Nerdtool)
What does this Pull Request (PR) do?
Corrects the command in the readme instruction
How should this be manually tested?
N/A
Any background context you can provide?
The command doesn't seem like it would have ever done anything useful, TBH. I'd guess this was mistakenly written at some point. It is possible that this was mistakenly omitted as the first step, in which case it might make sense to add it previous to the search rather than replace it.
What are the relevant tickets (if any)?
N/A
